dct_title_s: Map of Oberon showing land located in Longport, N.J. owned by Oberon Investment & Development Co.
dct_description_sm: Map shows the property of Oberon Investment and Development Co. highlighted in pink and the numbered town lots in the city of Longport. Map covers area from Twenty-Fourth Avenue to Colorado Avenue along the Atlantic Ocean.
